<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-title>Architecting for the Next Peak</mj-title>
    <!-- Montserrat Font Import from Style Guide -->
    <mj-font
      name="Montserrat"
      href="https://www.google.com/search?q=https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2%3Ffamily%3DMontserrat:wght%40400%3B600%3B800%26display%3Dswap"
    />
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-all font-family="Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" />
      <mj-text font-size="16px" color="#242424" line-height="1.6" />
      <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="0" />
      <mj-button
        background-color="#d72323"
        color="#ffffff"
        font-size="14px"
        font-weight="600"
        text-transform="uppercase"
        inner-padding="18px 36px"
        border-radius="0px"
      />
    </mj-attributes>
    <mj-style inline="inline">
      .logo-white { color: #efefef; } .logo-red { color: #d72323; }
    </mj-style>
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body background-color="#efefef">
    <!-- Header / Logo Section -->
    <mj-section background-color="#000000" padding="20px 0px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
          src="https://us-west-2.graphassets.com/cm9jgdu600q7l07n2379r6hbk/cmlbdmue5at8407n1kass3l6d"
          width="300px"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Hero Image Section -->
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
          src="img/hero.png"
          alt="Mountain clibmers looking off into the distance at the next peak they want to climb, symbolizing the concept of 'architecting for the next peak' in business and resilience."
          padding="0"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Welcome Content Section -->
    <mj-section padding="20px 40px 20px 40px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          font-size="28px"
          font-weight="800"
          line-height="1.2"
          text-transform="uppercase"
          padding-bottom="20px"
          color="#d72323"
        >
          Architecting for the Next Peak
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text> Hi {firstName}, </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          Success at one level can often mask the fragility required for the
          next. As you look toward your next stage of growth, I want to
          pressure-test your architecture:
          <ol>
            <li>
              <strong>The Stress Test:</strong> If you doubled volume tomorrow, where would the
              "crack" appear?
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>The Sustainability Test:</strong> How much success is tied to intuition vs.
              repeatable systems?
            </li>
          </ol>
          The goal isn't to fix what is brokenâ€”it's to ensure your foundation
          can hold the weight of your future ambitions.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          Schedule a strategy session and let's architect for the next peak
          together.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>Talk Soon,</mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          Dom DeStasio <br />
          <em>Co-Founder &amp; CEO, ForceBuilders</em>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px 50px 40px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-button
          href="https://forcebuilders.link/strategy-session"
          align="center"
        >
          SCHEDULE NOW
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Highlight / Feature Section -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px 40px 40px">
      <mj-column
        border-left="6px solid #d72323"
        background-color="#efefef"
        padding="30px"
      >
        <mj-text font-size="14px" padding="0">
          Don't forget to check out our upcoming webinar.
          <a
            href="https://forcebuilders.link/webinar"
            style="color: #d72323; font-weight: 600"
            >Register now</a
          >.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <mj-section background-color="#000000" padding="40px 40px">
      <mj-column>
        <!-- Logo Mark -->
        <mj-image
          src="https://us-west-2.graphassets.com/cm9jgdu600q7l07n2379r6hbk/cmlbefs8vbg9t07n1rm8n9t3o"
          width="40px"
        />
        <mj-text
          color="#efefef"
          font-size="11px"
          align="center"
          padding-bottom="20px"
        >
          ForceBuilders, LLC <br />
          1675 Route 228 #1054 <br />
          Cranberry Township, PA 16066 <br />
          (412) 212-3210
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="11px" padding-bottom="30px">
          <a
            href="https://forcebuilders.link/linkedin-forcebuilders"
            style="color: #d72323; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600"
          >
            <img
              src="https://us-west-2.graphassets.com/cm9jgdu600q7l07n2379r6hbk/cmlbmqf05mdam07n1mzud6tx0"
              style="width: 15px"
            />
          </a>
          &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;
          <a
            href="https://forcebuilders.link/forcebuilders-insta"
            style="color: #d72323; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600"
          >
            <img
              src="https://us-west-2.graphassets.com/cm9jgdu600q7l07n2379r6hbk/cmlbmqex1lnjt07myo2vlh3gj"
              style="width: 15px"
            />
          </a>
          &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;
          <a href="https://forcebuilders.com" style="text-decoration: none">
            <img
              src="https://us-west-2.graphassets.com/cm9jgdu600q7l07n2379r6hbk/cmlbmqeqgmd9w07n164nd78u8"
              style="width: 15px"
            />
          </a>
          &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;
          <a href="https://forcebuilders.link/linktree">
            <img
              src="https://us-west-2.graphassets.com/cm9jgdu600q7l07n2379r6hbk/cmlbmqet7mdaf07n18jwpl0gs"
              style="width: 15px"
            />
          </a>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#efefef" font-size="10px" align="center">
          &copy; 2026 ForceBuilders. All rights reserved.<br />
          <a
            href="{unsubscribe_link}"
            style="color: #efefef; text-decoration: underline"
            >Unsubscribe</a
          >
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
